Reference.description:
A reference to a style definition.

Use as value `attrs` to reference value from `definitions`.

Example of usage:
```json
{
   "definitions": {
     "roadColor": { "type": "color", "value": "#f00" }
   },
   "styles": { "tilezen": [
      {
       "when": "kind == 'road",
       "technique": "solid-line",
       "attr": {
         "lineColor": { "$ref": "roadColor" }
       }
     }
   ] }
}
```
